reviewText: This video is thoroughly enjoyable!  It has a great music track, narration, and video and still photography.  All ages find it a nice comfortable watch getting ready for bed.  Nicely done!  Good bit of history, too.
I  have this on VHS so when I saw it on amazon had to download it. The views of the lighthouses  are so beautiful you see so many LH that can only be scene by air.
This was a gift and they truly love it ! ! !
Excellant tour of these lighthouses. Great DVD if your into Lighthouses. Thankfully there are some still available. Hopefully there will be more.
We wouldn't have minded if this video was longer but we sure enjoy what is here.  Worth the money.
